data.description: Discover the epitome of luxury living in this expansive one-story home sprawled across over 5 acres of picturesque land, boasting breathtaking views of the downtown San Antonio skyline. With 4 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and 2 half bathrooms, this residence offers spaciousness and versatility. Additional bonuses include two elegant office rooms featuring French doors for privacy, as well as a delightful playroom that seamlessly connects to the kitchen. Throughout the home, built-in desk and workspace areas provide convenience and functionality. The open floor plan bathes the interior in natural light, creating an inviting ambiance. The kitchen stands as a culinary haven with a vast breakfast bar, island, gas cooktop, and abundant cabinet space. The primary bedroom is a retreat, complete with a fireplace and an ensuite that features dual vanities, a soaking tub, a walk-in shower, and a capacious walk-in closet with custom built-ins. Outside, the immense backyard presents endless possibilities - relax on the covered patio while taking in the remarkable view, or work in your 12x20 workshop with a mini split hvac system. The opportunities are truly boundless - don't miss your chance to explore this remarkable property!
